</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Nonprofit Organization</h1>
            <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Donations</a>
            <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Volunteer Registration</a>
            <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Event Listings</a>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="card">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Welcome to our Nonprofit Organization</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">We are a nonprofit organization dedicated to making a difference in the world. We believe in the power of community and strive to create a better world for all. Join us in our mission to make a difference.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Donations</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">We rely on the generosity of our community to continue our work. Your donation can make a significant difference.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Volunteer Registration</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">We are always looking for volunteers to help us in our mission. Whether you're a seasoned professional or a first-time volunteer, we'd love to have you.</p>
